    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class OtaDefaultBleManagerConfig
extends BleManagerConfig
    Default instance of BleManagerConfig with some options set for optimal OTA performance. NOTE: Callbacks will not be guaranteed to be on the main thread (unles otherwise configured by subclassing this class). This helps to cut down on thread switching.
